# Reasoning

The issue is asking to update the Maven Compiler plugin in the `pom.xml` file to use a specific version and configuration. The provided code snippet shows the required changes.

To address this issue, we need to add the specified properties and plugin configuration to the `pom.xml` file.

First, we add the properties section with the specified versions:

```xml
<properties>
    <compiler-plugin.version>3.10.1</compiler-plugin.version>
    <maven.compiler.release>11</maven.compiler.release>
</properties>
```

Next, we update the build section to include the Maven Compiler plugin with the specified version and configuration:

```xml
<build>
    <plugins>
        <plugin>
            <artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>
            <version>${compiler-plugin.version}</version>
            <configuration>
                <compilerArgs>
                    <arg>-parameters</arg>
                </compilerArgs>
            </configuration>
        </plugin>
    </plugins>
</build>
```

We also need to update the existing `maven-compiler-plugin` section to use the new version and configuration.
